					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1667" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ana-martin-ajByNgzbklo-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ana-martin-ajByNgzbklo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ana-martin-ajByNgzbklo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C500&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ana-martin-ajByNgzbklo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1000&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ana-martin-ajByNgzbklo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1333&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ana-martin-ajByNgzbklo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=224%2C146&amp;ssl=1 224w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ana-martin-ajByNgzbklo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導 你有看過這麼不想穿鞋子的狗狗嗎？美國一名飼主前幾日為自家狗狗「Milo」準備了 &#8230;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/22/%e5%b0%b1%e6%98%af%e4%b8%8d%e6%83%b3%e7%a9%bf%e9%9b%a8%e9%9e%8b%ef%bc%9f%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e4%b8%8b%e9%9b%a8%e5%a4%a9%e6%95%a3%e6%ad%a5%e7%a9%bf%e9%9e%8b%e7%ab%9f%e7%9b%b4%e6%8e%a5%e8%ba%ba%e5%b9%b3/">就是不想穿雨鞋？狗狗下雨天散步穿鞋竟直接躺平 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
