										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1667" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ana-martin-ajByNgzbklo-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ana-martin-ajByNgzbklo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ana-martin-ajByNgzbklo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C500&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ana-martin-ajByNgzbklo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1000&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ana-martin-ajByNgzbklo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1333&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ana-martin-ajByNgzbklo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=224%2C146&amp;ssl=1 224w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ana-martin-ajByNgzbklo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導</p>



<p>你有看過這麼不想穿鞋子的狗狗嗎？美國一名飼主前幾日為自家狗狗「Milo」準備了一雙雨鞋，原本只是想在濕滑天氣裡保護愛犬的腳掌，卻沒想到意外引發一連串爆笑反應，瞬間吸引大量網友的關注與轉發。&nbsp;</p>



<p>原來這名飼主在某天中午觀看天氣預報時，得知當地未來的幾天都會著下大雨，於是特地為愛犬購入了一雙專門為狗狗設計的雨鞋，打算在之後的雨天裡出門散步使用。&nbsp;</p>



<p>但由於「Milo」在過去未曾穿過鞋子，因此這雙雨鞋成為了牠全新的挑戰，當鞋子剛套上狗狗的腳時，「Milo」就顯得極度不適應，不僅連基本走路都變得困難重重，甚至連站起身來都有問題。&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="794" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ana-martin-ajByNgzbklo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C794&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-230290" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ana-martin-ajByNgzbklo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ana-martin-ajByNgzbklo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C500&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ana-martin-ajByNgzbklo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1000&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ana-martin-ajByNgzbklo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1333&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ana-martin-ajByNgzbklo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=224%2C146&amp;ssl=1 224w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ana-martin-ajByNgzbklo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">「Milo」穿上雨鞋後完全無法走路，最後乾脆直接躺平放棄<br>(示意圖/Unsplash)</figcaption></figure>



<p>「Milo」穿上雨鞋後的反應也讓飼主爆笑，起初狗狗展現出相當困惑的行走模式，牠緩慢地抬高四肢，一臉茫然地步伐僵硬，彷彿踩在陌生的地板上，試圖理解這雙雨鞋的存在，但最終還是乾脆直接躺平放棄。&nbsp;</p>



<p>飼主將「Milo」穿雨鞋的趣事分享到網路上，引起了許多網友熱烈討論，不少人紛紛留言「狗狗感覺很無奈」、「牠可能以為主人在惡作劇」、「雨鞋白買了」、「還是腳踏實地最好」。&nbsp;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/22/%e5%b0%b1%e6%98%af%e4%b8%8d%e6%83%b3%e7%a9%bf%e9%9b%a8%e9%9e%8b%ef%bc%9f%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e4%b8%8b%e9%9b%a8%e5%a4%a9%e6%95%a3%e6%ad%a5%e7%a9%bf%e9%9e%8b%e7%ab%9f%e7%9b%b4%e6%8e%a5%e8%ba%ba%e5%b9%b3/">就是不想穿雨鞋？狗狗下雨天散步穿鞋竟直接躺平 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
